Morgan Brittany https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Morgan_Brittany 0 Morgan Brittany (born Suzanne Cupito; December 5, 1951) is an American actress, best known for her role as Katherine Wentworth, the scheming younger half-sister of Pamela Ewing and Cliff Barnes, on the prime-time soap opera Dallas.
